article.description: — Mekhi Long had 19 points and 19 points in Old Dominion's 60-59 win over Coastal Carolina on Saturday night.
article.headline: Old Dominion knocks off Coastal Carolina 60-59
article.linkText: Old Dominion knocks off Coastal Carolina 60-59
article.story:
CONWAY, S.C. -- — Mekhi Long had 19 points and 19 points in Old Dominion's 60-59 win over Coastal Carolina on Saturday night.

Bryce Baker made two free throws with one second left to put the Monarchs up 60-59. He scored nine points and added seven rebounds for Old Dominion (13-9, 5-5 Sun Belt Conference).

Josh Uduje finished with 18 points, nine rebounds and four steals for the Chanticleers (10-12, 4-6). Coastal Carolina also got 13 points and seven rebounds from Essam Mostafa. Linton Brown also had 13 points.

------
